torrentkino (0.15) wheezy; urgency=low

  * New Tumbleweed default: Run on port TCP/80 instead of TCP/8080 if started by root
  * New Torrentkino default: Announce port 80 instead of 8080 if started by root
  * Torrentkino: 1 core => 1 thread. Tumbleweed: 1 core => 2 threads.
  * Multicast cleanup
  * Bootstrap port cleanup
  * IP code cleanup

 -- Aiko Barz <aiko@chroot.de>  Wed, 06 Oct 2013 22:21:00 +0100
